    "Threat Value, TV (Sec. IV-B) \u2014 discrete distance bands to the nearest asset, exactly as defined in the paper: TV \u2208 {1, 0.9, 0.7, 0.5, 0} for {very close, close, medium, far, very far}, rather than a continuous gradient."
